track_notes: Follow the path in front of the Pub and through the Farm yard. A good path all the way to the top.
This track is the full track to the Trig Point and the highest point on the summit. The start is at Litton. All the flat summit is in the activation Zone.
track_title: Both summits in the activation area

track_notes: Public CP (Pay and Display). Follow roads to SD 9363 7746.  Then turn left (S) onto bridle way.  Uphill to SD 9334 7680, where I took a direct line to the low point on the ridge above.  No proper path, but some sheep tracks.  Steep at the headwall.  Cross broken wall at SD 9210 7614 and join path, turning right (NW) to summit.
track_title: From the CP in Buckden village
